  "title": "IDrawingDoc.ActiveDrawingView",
  "description": "Gets the currently active drawing view.",
  "signature": "System.Object ActiveDrawingView {get;}",
  "parameters": [],
  "returns": "Currently active drawing view",
  "remarks": "This property returns the active drawing view, if one is active. If the drawing sheet is active, the property returns NULL and you can use\nIDrawingDoc::GetCurrentSheet\nto get the current sheet for this drawing.\nThis is a read-only property. Use\nIDrawingDoc::ActivateView\nto set the active drawing view.",
